"""
FinPulse — Agent 4: EXECUTIVE NARRATIVE ENGINE
===============================================
The final agent in the pipeline. Takes all prior agent outputs and
produces board-ready, regulator-ready, plain-English narratives.

Fundamental difference from Agents 1, 2, 3:

  Agent 1  →  DETECTION:    Isolation Forest scores, ML flags, rule triggers
  Agent 2  →  INVESTIGATION: Per-account chat, transaction evidence
  Agent 3  →  ASSESSMENT:   Systemic risk classification, regulatory decision
  Agent 4  →  NARRATIVE:    Plain English story for non-technical decision makers

Audience: Chief Compliance Officer, Board Risk Committee, Regulators, Press Office
NOT for: Data scientists, analysts, compliance investigators (that was Agents 1-3)

Key differentiators:
  - Three distinct narrative modes: BOARD / REGULATOR / PRESS
  - No jargon — translates all technical findings into business language
  - Action items with owners and deadlines — not just findings
  - The IBM AML market correlation story told as a business narrative
  - Downloadable plain-text report
  - Visual pipeline summary showing all 4 agents contributing
  - Industry benchmark comparisons to contextualise findings
"""

